OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,GThe early days of the new year mark
OL,7,Gthe 40th anniversary of the death of
OL,8,G405-line TV in the UK.
OL,10,FThe last BBC and IBA 405-line masts
OL,11,Fwere switched off in the early hours
OL,12,Fof 3rd and 4th January 1985.
OL,13,F(Apparently the BBC's Scottish
OL,14,Ftransmitters were turned off on the
OL,15,F4th because of the extra bank holiday
OL,16,Fat New Year north of the border.)
OL,18,FBut by then, virtually nobody was
OL,19,Fwatching 405-line sets.
OL,21,FThe BBC estimated that only around 700
OL,22,Fwere still in use.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/9
