OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,FThe BBC and IBA received few comments
OL,7,Ffrom concerned viewers even though the
OL,8,Fswitch-off had been publicised through
OL,9,Fon-screen captions.
OL,11,FIn other words, 405-line was kept
OL,12,Fgoing until virtually nobody would
OL,13,Flose out when it was turned off.
OL,15,FThose who predict quick ends to major
OL,16,Fservices today would be wise to
OL,17,Fconsider this.
OL,19,FThe writing was on the wall for 405-
OL,20,Fline TV for more than 20 years.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/9
