OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,FThe only people to lose out were
OL,7,Fexceptional examples.
OL,9,FFor instance, a few remote communities
OL,10,For isolated homes could only pick up a
OL,11,FVHF signal. Most though were covered
OL,12,Fby relays or local self-help schemes
OL,13,Fby then.
OL,15,FSo what has all this got to do with
OL,16,Fthe present day?
OL,18,FFirst of all Radio 4 LW may finally go
OL,19,Foff the air in June. But this date
OL,20,Fcould still slip.
