OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,FEnergy companies have been contacting
OL,7,Fcustomers whose meters are controlled
OL,8,Fby a signal transmitted alongside R4
OL,9,FLW.
OL,11,FConcern for these customers has kept
OL,12,Flong wave radio on the air.
OL,14,FIf it becomes apparent that the June
OL,15,Fdeadline will not be met by energy
OL,16,Fcompanies, do not rule out a further
OL,17,Fpostponement.
