OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,FAs for those who imagine linear TV
OL,7,Fitself is dead, I would refer them to
OL,8,Fmy recent piece on the Christmas
OL,9,Fratings.
OL,11,FThis week, it was incredible to see
OL,12,Fthat 5.1m watched the first episode of
OL,13,Fthe new series of The Traitors on BBC
OL,14,FOne ` well up on last year's debut.
OL,16,FThere is speculation though that
OL,17,FFreeview could lose its HD service.
OL,19,FBut would Ofcom and the government
OL,20,Freally sit by and let this happen?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/9
