OL,3,C405-line switch-off and similarities
OL,4,Cwith present day service closures
OL,6,FPredicting the future is a risky
OL,7,Fbusiness.
OL,9,FA universal public service broadcaster
OL,10,Fcan find itself doing things for a
OL,11,Flong time for the sake of the
OL,12,Fvulnerable.
OL,14,FWould switching off VHF in, say, 1980
OL,15,Fhave affected many? I doubt it.
OL,17,FWill BBC Four and CBBC go this year? I
OL,18,Fdoubt it too.
